metadata.name: Moonshot #2 - Lonely - ULTRA-RARE DIAMOND EDITION
metadata.description:
This rare, 1 of 1 token can only be obtained by collecting 9 Moonshot tokens with each of the different frames.

MOONSHOT is a music NFT collection based on 5 songs written by Violetta Zironi and 2500 unique, hand-drawn artworks by Giuseppe Zironi (Violetta's dad), a renowned Disney illustrator for over 30 years.

The songs were co-written by Violetta with multi platinum songwriter Michael Ochs, and produced with 2x Grammy winning producer Matt Rollings.

Find out more about the music here:
[Violetta Zironi](https://www.violettazironi.com/)

Each song was inspired by a real life situation that occurred in Violetta’s life. Each artwork was inspired by the songs.

The music will take you somewhere you’ve never been, but yet feels familiar.
